Abaard House Publishing

Bringing stories to life and empowering voices through exceptional publishing services.

About Us

Founded in Toronto, Abaard House Publishing is a forward-thinking publishing company dedicated to discovering and nurturing diverse voices. Our mission is to provide authors with the resources and support they need to share their stories with the world. We combine traditional editorial excellence with innovative digital strategies to ensure every publication reaches its full potential.

Our Services

Manuscript Editing

Our experienced editors work closely with authors to refine and polish manuscripts, ensuring clarity, coherence, and compelling storytelling.

Book Design

From cover concept to interior layout, our design team creates visually stunning books that capture the essence of each story.

Distribution

We partner with global distributors and retailers to make your book available worldwide, both in print and digital formats.
